          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1666779381034-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the potato wedges are cooking, combine your<strong> lean pork mince</strong> (remove the paper if required!), <strong>‘Nduja</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>panko breadcrumbs </strong>in a bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong> and stir it all together until the 'Nduja and breadcrumbs are fully incorporated</p><p>Divide the<strong> mixture</strong> equally and shape into 3 meatballs per person</p>",
