    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>meatballs</strong> to a separate baking tray (use <strong>baking paper</strong> to avoid mess!) and put the tray in the oven for 15 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Boil half a kettle</p>",
