    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the meatballs are done, transfer them to the thickened sauce and stir together until they're fully coated</p><p>Once the wedges are almost cooked, add the <strong>halved ciabatta</strong>, cut-side up, to the tray[s] and put in the oven for 1-2 min or until starting to crisp</p><p>Tip: This will stop them from going soggy when you add the meatballs!</p>",
