    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once starting to crisp, top the bottom of the <strong>ciabatta</strong> with the <strong>meatballs</strong> and any remaining<strong> sauce</strong></p><p>Top the <strong>meatballs</strong> with the<strong> grated cheese</strong> and return the tray to the oven for 3-4 min further or until the cheese has melted – this is your <strong>spicy lean pork & 'Nduja meatball ciabatta</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> salad</strong>, then pat it dry with<strong> </strong>kitchen paper</p>",
